projects.projectDetails: JDA Cloud Central application develope on top of Angularjs, sharepoint list. It's a completely dynamic application. All the contents comes from the SP list and images also load dynamicaly from the SP Document. This application is design about the Cloud Central which help the customer to undersand more about the company in cloud.
projects.role:
As a UX designers and UI Developer are primarily concerned with how the product feels. A given design problem has no single right answer. Explore many different approaches to solving a specific user problem. The broad responsibility is to ensure that the product logically flows from one step to the next. One way that to do this is by conducting in-person user tests to observe one's behavior. By identifying verbal and non-verbal stumbling blocks, refine and iterate to create the "best" user experience.

I’ve been lucky enough to be contributing to defining roles and just where people like me will sit within our structure at work. I've usally follow the development process, there are three phases: “Design”, “Design Implementation”, and Application Development
keyPoint: Testing the responsive & behaviour of app
